{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Although the statute required only \u8220\'3fentry to campuses,\u8221\'3f the federal government, after the September 11, 2001 terrorist attacks, adopted an informal policy of \u8220\'3frequir[ing] universities to provide military recruiters access to students equal in quality and scope to that provided to other recruiters.\u8221\'3f
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
