23
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 The Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit agreed with the District Court, holding that FAIR had associational standing to bring the suit on behalf of its members.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
