24
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 It also held, contrary to the District Court, that the Solomon Amendment regulated speech in addition to expressive conduct.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
