25
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 The Third Circuit thus reversed and remanded to the District Court, ordering it to enter a preliminary injunction against enforcement of the Solomon 
