{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0ESGAG_1}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0ESGAG_1}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Prior Supreme Court precedent has established the principle that freedom of speech prohibits the government from telling individuals what they must say.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F103333572300_ID0E2GAG_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F103333572300_ID0E2GAG_1}
