108
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 The Court agreed that some precedent supported the belief that the government is limited in its ability to force a speaker to host or accommodate another speaker\rquote s message.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
