{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 the Court found that state law cannot require a parade to include a group whose message the parade\rquote s organizer does not wish to send.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F111333572300_ID0E4IAG_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F111333572300_ID0E4IAG_1}
