{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
In this case, however, the Court distinguished those prior decisions, noting that in those cases, the burdened party\rquote s own message was negatively affected by the speech it was forced to accommodate.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F114333572300_ID0ETJAG_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F114333572300_ID0ETJAG_1}
