114
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 For instance, in Hurley, the Court found that the expressive nature of parades was a critical fact in their decision\u8212\'3fthat parades by their very nature are expressive and convey a message.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
