{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 In this case, accommodating the military recruiter\rquote s message did not affect the law schools\rquote  speech because the schools were not speaking when they allowed recruiters on campus.
}
