{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Because the law schools\rquote  job placement programs wholly lacked any expressive quality of a parade or other channels of conveying a message, the accommodation of the federal law did not sufficiently interfere with any message of the school.
}
